PersonalMission.Name: SPG-13: C for Cooperation
PersonalMission.Description: Strong cooperation between SPGs and allies should make the enemy team extremely worried. Coordinate your actions and focus your fire on one enemy target at a time.

Primary.Conditions:
Cause damage 6 times (personal/Platoon)
or
  Stun 8 times (Personal/Platoon)
